snippet.title: Introducing AdVenture Ages | Available NOW on AppStore and Google Play!
snippet.description:
Download AdVenture Ages here: https://bit.ly/AgesYTDL

Introducing AdVenture Ages! 

Congratulations - you’ve saved all of time! At least, you did, before coffee spilled in the time machine. Transported back to past civilizations, you’ll need to restore history and rebuild your glittering career before your Utopian future ceases to exist. 

Looking for tips, agents? Follow us on the following channels:

Facebook Page: http://bit.ly/AdAgesFB
Twitter: http://bit.ly/AdAgesTW
Instagram: http://bit.ly/AdAgesIG
Reddit: http://bit.ly/AdAgesRI
Discord: http://bit.ly/AdAgesDC
